### Crear nuevo perfil
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "DNI": "987654321",
    "name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "date_birthday": "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "national": "Peru",
    "phone": "987654321",
    "addres": "Test Address 123",
    "sex": "M",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "id_user": 1
}

### Obtener todos los perfiles
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles


### Obtener perfil por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/1


### Actualizar perfil
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profiles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Updated",
    "phone": "999888777"
}

### Eliminar perfil (borrado l√≥gico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/profiles/1


